Race.SpecificTitle: City of Jeanerette -- 3.75 Mills - Mayor & BOA - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the City of Jeanerette, State of Louisiana (the "City"), levy a special tax of three and seventy-five hundredths (3.75) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the City (an estimated $57,750 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2016 and ending with the year 2025, for the purposes of constructing, improving, maintaining and resurfacing public streets in the City, including acquiring, maintaining and operating equipment therefor, and supporting the general fund?
